%% Data Flow Diagram - Kubeflow Trainer
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant APIServer as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as Trainer Controller<br/>(opendatahub namespace)
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pod (rank-0)<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>(PodMonitor)

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation

    User->>APIServer: kubectl apply TrainJob<br/>Bearer Token / Client Cert
    APIServer->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-...-trainjob<br/>AdmissionReview (API server client cert)
    Webhook-->>APIServer: Allowed / Denied
    APIServer-->>User: TrainJob created

    Controller->>APIServer: Watch TrainJob CRs<br/>ServiceAccount token
    APIServer-->>Controller: TrainJob event

    Controller->>APIServer: GET TrainingRuntime/ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>ServiceAccount token
    APIServer-->>Controller: Runtime spec

    Controller->>APIServer: CREATE JobSet<br/>ServiceAccount token
    APIServer-->>Controller: JobSet created

    Controller->>APIServer: CREATE NetworkPolicy<br/>ServiceAccount token
    APIServer-->>Controller: NetworkPolicy created

    opt Co-scheduling enabled
        Controller->>APIServer: CREATE PodGroup<br/>(Volcano/scheduler-plugins)
        APIServer-->>Controller: PodGroup created
    end

    JobSetCtrl->>APIServer: Watch JobSet CRs
    APIServer-->>JobSetCtrl: JobSet event
    JobSetCtrl->>APIServer: CREATE Jobs/Pods

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: Progression Tracking (RHAI Feature)

    Controller->>APIServer: LIST Pods (APIReader)<br/>ServiceAccount token
    APIServer-->>Controller: Pod list with IPs

    Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP 28080/TCP plaintext<br/>NetworkPolicy-restricted
    TrainingPod-->>Controller: JSON {progressPercentage, currentStep, ...}

    Controller->>APIServer: PATCH TrainJob annotations<br/>ServiceAccount token
    APIServer-->>Controller: Updated

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Monitoring

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS 8443/TCP TLS<br/>PodMonitor scrape
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
